title: United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Silk
description: Imports of Intra EU - Silk in the United Kingdom increased to 0.82 GBP Million in September from 0.70 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Intra EU - Silk in the United Kingdom averaged 1.57 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 9.61 GBP Million in April of 1997 and a record low of 0.22 GBP Million in February of 2021. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Silk.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
